lead_paragraph: World champions Germany will not attempt to break a 104-year-old goalscoring record when they take on lowly San Marino in their World Cup qualifier on Friday, coach Joachim Loew said.

headline.print_headline: Goal Record Is Not Germany's Aim Against San Marino-Loew
